text: Diadelia atomosparsa is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Fairmaire in 1904.BioLib.cz - Diadelia atomosparsa. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Diadelia Category:Beetles described in 1904 Category:Taxa named by Léon Fairmaire
